# Feature Engineering

This section documents my journey of learning Feature Engineering.

Feature Engineering is one of the most important steps in Machine Learning, as the quality of features often determines the quality of the model.

Current Focus:
- Handling Missing Values
- Encoding Categorical Variables
- Feature Scaling
- Outlier Treatment
- Feature Selection
- Feature Extraction
- Date & Time Features
- Text Features
- Dimensionality Reduction
To learn how to transform raw data into meaningful features that improve machine learning model performance.
